Subject: [PATCH] bnxt: don't enable NAPI until rings are ready
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.8.8
Git-commit: 96ecdcc992eb7f468b2cf829b0f5408a1fad4668

[ Upstream commit 96ecdcc992eb7f468b2cf829b0f5408a1fad4668 ]

